   Can someone tell me where I can find docs to write a frame buffer 
   driver ?
AFAIK there aren't any real docs beyond those in Documentation/fb.
When I was writing a VGA 16-color framebuffer driver I found the
source code to other framebuffer drivers for Linux to be the best
reference.
